-- China Steel Investment Still High, Association’s Zhang Says
-- B y   H e l e n   Y u a n
-- 2011-12-17T01:46:53Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-12-17/china-steel-investment-still-high-association-s-zhang-says.html
Investment in  China ’s steel industry
remains high even as companies are struggling to make profits,
said Zhang Changfu, vice chairman and secretary general
of the China Iron and Steel Association. Investment in the
industry from non-state-owned companies was twice that from
state companies in the January to October period of this year,
Zhang said at a Mysteel.com conference today in  Shanghai .  To contact the reporter on this story:
Helen Yuan in Shanghai at 
